snippet.title: Porle Mone | Awara | Jeet | Sayantika | Jeet Gannguli | Bengali | 2012

localized.description:
Presnting Porle Mone from Awara starring Jeet and Sayantika. This song has been composed and sung by Jeet Gannguli. 

Film : Awara
Starring : Jeet, Sayantika, Ashish Vidyarthi, Mukul Dev & others.
Producer : Shree Venkatesh Films.
Presenter : Shrikant Mohta & Mahendra Soni
Direction : Ravi Kinnagi
Music: Jeet Ganguly
Singer : Jeet Ganguly
